search_results.title: Uriah Connors - Biography
search_results.snippet: Uriah Connors is known for GCW Til Infinity (2022), GCW Hope to Die (2022) and JCW BattleBowl the Lethal Lottery (2023).

search_results.title: Uriah Connors - Facts @ Wrestlingdata.com
search_results.snippet: Uriah Connors is the son of Dave Finlay, the grandson of David Finlay and the brother of David Finlay Jr. Tag Teams, Air BnB with Bobby Flaco (as Brogan Finlay).
